Fixed device credential resolution for NUTS verification and deployment jobs. Credentials are now resolved per device using the SecretsGroup assigned directly to the device record in Nautobot (SSH access type), falling back to the global `device_secrets_group` configured in `PLUGINS_CONFIG`, then to `DEVICE_USERNAME`/`DEVICE_PASSWORD` environment variables as a last resort. Previously the code incorrectly used `access_type="Generic"` when querying SecretsGroups, causing a silent exception and unconditional fallback to environment variables even when `device_secrets_group` was configured.
